title: Teen whose parents ‘cut her off because she has a black boyfriend’ raises three times more than original £10k target for her tuition fees
text:
Opinion TAKE THAT MUM AND DAD Teen whose parents ‘cut her off because she has a black boyfriend’ raises three times more than original £10k target for her tuition fees 
Allie Dowdle, 18, has raised almost £30k after claiming her parents took away her college fund, phone and car over beau BY MARNIE O'NEILL FOR NEWS.COM.AU 11th February 2017, 12:01 am
